---
title: Smart Zesty Plant-Based Ground Protein Meatballs with Lemon-Garlic Sauce and Mini Wedges
description: Lemon zest gives these plant-based ground protein meatballs bright flavour and provides a nice counterpoint to the garlic sauce. The creamy dill dressing on the salad gives off Mediterranean vibes, while the mini potato wedges are just adorable.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R1026_W39_CA_RC158363-1_Main_low-9ac14001.jpg
